.Ve
.IP "new_with_args" 4
.IX Item "new_with_args"
Although v1 calls will continue to work, this is not supported in v2, for it
is a trivial application of \f(CW\*(C`new_with_init\*(C'\fR.
.IP "new_with_init" 4
.IX Item "new_with_init"
.Vb 2
